              <h3 className="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-2">Laboratory Monitoring</h3>
              <div className="text-blue-800 text-sm space-y-1">
                <p>â€¢ <strong>Baseline:</strong> Total T, Free T, E2, SHBG, CBC, CMP, PSA</p>
                <p>â€¢ <strong>6-8 weeks:</strong> Total T, Free T, E2 (adjust dose if needed)</p>
                <p>â€¢ <strong>3-6 months:</strong> Full panel including lipids, HbA1c</p>
                <p>â€¢ <strong>Ongoing:</strong> Every 6-12 months or as clinically indicated</p>
                <p>â€¢ <strong>Timing:</strong> Draw labs at trough (just before next injection)</p>
